## 5. Document Pipeline Рђћ Stage Map

| Stage | What | Status |
|-------|------|--------|
| 1 | `POST /documents/upload` Рђћ accept PDF, validate, store, metadata row | РюЁ Done |
| 2 | `GET /documents/{id}` Рђћ status polling endpoint | РюЁ Done |
| 3 | PDF text extraction + chunking (background worker) | РЮї Next |
| 4 | Embed chunks Рєњ store in Pinecone with `document_id` metadata | РЮї Next |
| 5 | Query planner agent (Option B: metadata filter Рєњ targeted Pinecone search) | РЮї Future |
| 6 | Multi-source synthesis (PDF + SQL + API Рєњ LLM answer) | РЮї Future |

**Document status lifecycle:** `pending_processing Рєњ processing Рєњ completed | failed`

